# General

- Prefer immutable css. Use inline `tailwind` classes. 
- Prefer the `zinc` family of colors. Add color only when requested. 
- Use `lucide-react` for icons.
- Use `clsx` for style variants or to apply css classes conditionally
- Use `framer-motion` to animate elements.
- Add new components into `/src/components`.
- Add new images, fonts, videos, or other  assets into `/src/assets`.
- For placeholder and fake data, generate it randomly or use `faker`

